{"id":4283,"date":"2025-06-19T11:52:18","date_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:52:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4283"},"modified":"2025-06-19T11:52:18","modified_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:52:18","slug":"top-cac-hoat-chat-lam-mo-tham-mun","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/top-cac-hoat-chat-lam-mo-tham-mun\/","title":{"rendered":"Top c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m m\u1edd th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t 2025"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m m\u1edd th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t sau khi m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf v\u1ebft th\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn. R\u1ea5t may, hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da. C\u00f9ng GSC \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 10 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ecb th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tham-mun-la-gi\"><\/span><strong>Th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1ebft th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean da, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n sau khi m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0nh. Khi da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1eeb v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng do m\u1ee5n g\u00e2y ra, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 melanin \u2013 ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 trong da.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4348\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4348\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4348\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-1.webp\" alt=\"Th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4348\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft th\u00e2m kh\u00f3 phai, l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u v\u00e0 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-hop-cac-thanh-phan-hoat-chat-lam-mo-tham-mun-tot-nhat\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m m\u1edd th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m m\u1edd v\u1ebft th\u00e2m, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m m\u1edd th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"niacinamide-vitamin-b3\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide (Vitamin B3)<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Vitamin B3, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da. N\u00f3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da, thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4349\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4349\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4349\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-2.webp\" alt=\"Niacinamide (Vitamin B3)\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4349\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Niacinamide (Vitamin B3)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Niacinamide c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m m\u1edd v\u1ebft th\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, Niacinamide ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"centella-asiatica-rau-ma\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Centella Asiatica (Rau M\u00e1)<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Centella Asiatica, hay rau m\u00e1, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eefa l\u00e0nh v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, Centella Asiatica gi\u00fap l\u00e0m m\u1edd v\u1ebft th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap da tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4352\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4352\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4352\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-5.webp\" alt=\"Centella Asiatica (Rau M\u00e1)\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4352\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Centella Asiatica (Rau M\u00e1)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"azelaic-acid\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Azelaic Acid<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Azelaic Acid l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m m\u1edd th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzyme tyrosinase, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh melanin g\u00e2y s\u1ea1m da. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ee9a s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 d\u01b0 th\u1eeba, Azelaic Acid gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00f9ng da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u. Ngo\u00e0i ra, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Azelaic Acid mang \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da an to\u00e0n, d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4350\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4350\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4350\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-3.webp\" alt=\"Azelaic Acid\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4350\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Azelaic Acid<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"alpha-arbutin\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Alpha arbutin<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Alpha Arbutin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da. Gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m s\u1ea3n sinh melanin. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m m\u1edd c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, Alpha Arbutin ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, gi\u00fap mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4351\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4351\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4351\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-4.webp\" alt=\"Alpha arbutin\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/58-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4351\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Alpha arbutin<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"aha-alpha-hydroxy-acid\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">AHA (Alpha Hydroxy Acid)<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">AHA, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Axit Alpha Hydroxy, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i axit t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u da. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp da ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, AHA gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u h\u01a1n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, AHA c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bha-beta-hydroxy-acid\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">BHA (Beta Hydroxy Acid)<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">BHA (Beta Hydroxy Acid) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e2m nh\u1eadp s\u00e2u v\u00e0o b\u00ean trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn t\u00edch t\u1ee5 v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft. Nh\u1edd t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, BHA g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da t\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do m\u1ee5n, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m m\u1edd v\u1ebft th\u00e2m b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh melanin. Khi l\u1edbp da c\u0169 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng l\u1edbp da m\u1edbi s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe, l\u00e0n da tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng h\u01a1n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"retinol\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Retinol<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Retinol l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e2m sau m\u1ee5n. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen, Retinol gi\u00fap l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m m\u1edd c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u00e2m, Retinol c\u00f2n g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, Retinol ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kojic-acid\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kojic acid<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kojic Acid l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba s\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh melanin, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m v\u00e0 n\u00e1m da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u00edch th\u00edch qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, Kojic Acid \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m m\u1edd c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u00e2m do m\u1ee5n. Mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vitamin-c\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin C<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin C l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia UV v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Vitamin C c\u00f2n k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da m\u1edbi, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1edd v\u1ebft th\u00e2m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7n nay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0n da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u1eeb Azelaic Acid, Retinol cho \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 Centella Asiatica. M\u1ed7i ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m m\u1edd v\u1ebft th\u00e2m. Gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00f9ng GSC \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 10 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ecb th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4353,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4283","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4283","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4283"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4283\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4354,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4283\/revisions\/4354"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4353"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4283"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4283"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4283"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}